nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE MOVING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD FAR TO THE EAST OF HAWAII...
summary: ...HENRIETTE MOVING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD FAR TO THE EAST OF HAWAII... As of 11:00 PM HST Tue Aug 05 the center of Henriette was located near 17.8, -128.2 with movement W at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1003 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
